sequenceDiagram
  participant PilotUI as Pilot Dashboard (React)
  participant API as FastAPI (:8000)
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant PassengerUI as Passenger Dashboard (React)

  PilotUI->>API: POST /api/pilot/assign-flight {pilot_email, icao24}
  API->>DB: UPSERT pilot_flight_assignments
  API-->>PilotUI: assignment saved + selected flight payload

  PassengerUI->>API: GET /api/pilot/shared-flights (poll)
  API->>DB: read pilot_flight_assignments
  API->>DB: cached pipeline read (no OpenSky live fetch)
  API-->>PassengerUI: sharedFlights[]

